# Express.js RESTful API

## Setup
npm install
npm start

## Environment Variables
Copy `.env.example` to `.env` and set:
PORT=3000
API_KEY=12345

## Endpoints
GET /api/products  
GET /api/products/:id  
POST /api/products  
PUT /api/products/:id  
DELETE /api/products/:id  
GET /api/products/stats  

Supports:
- Filtering: ?category=electronics  
- Search: ?search=phone  
- Pagination: ?page=2&limit=5  

## Example Request
POST /api/products  
Header: x-api-key: 12345  
Body:
{
  "name": "Phone",
  "description": "Smartphone",
  "price": 799,
  "category": "electronics",
  "inStock": true
}
